snippet.title: Life of cute animals is full of funny moments - Funny animal compilation
snippet.description:
Here is a compilation with some old animal video clips, but, you know how it is, old is gold! These animals are so funny and cute, I'm sure they can make anyone laugh! Just look at all these dogs, puppies, cats, kittens, bears, bunnies, rabbits, squirrel, kangaroos,... What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!

WANT TO SEE YOUR PET IN OUR COMPILATIONS?
Send your clips or links to: tigerlicensing@gmail.com

For more funny videos & pictures visit and like our Facebook page:
https://www.facebook.com/tigerstudiosfun
